  startingCodeHint: "-- Goal: Build a blue cross on the floor (y = -4).\r\n-- The
    cross lines are along the X axis OR the Z axis.\r\n\r\nfunction PlaceVoxel(x,
    y, z)\r\n  local color = 0\r\n\r\n  -- Check if we are on the floor level\r\n 
    if y == -4 then\r\n    -- TODO: Add a check inside this 'if'.\r\n    -- The block
    should be placed if x is 0 OR z is 0.\r\n       color = 0\r\n  end\r\n\r\n  return
    color\r\nend"
